{% doc %}
  @prompt
    **Project:** Advanced Customizable Privacy Policy Page for Shopify
    
    I want to create a **modern, visually stunning, and highly responsive Privacy Policy page** for my Shopify store. The page must work perfectly on **all devices and screen sizes** including mobile phones, tablets, laptops, and large desktop monitors.
    
    The goal is to transform a normally boring legal page into a **premium, beautifully animated, and interactive experience**, while keeping the content clear and easy to read.
    
    ---
    
    ## Design & Visual Style
    
    The page should have a **clean, elegant, and modern UI** with a strong focus on **glassmorphism design**.
    
    Each section should appear as a **glass-style panel/card** with:
    
    * Semi-transparent glass background
    * Backdrop blur effect
    * Soft subtle borders
    * Smooth shadows
    * Rounded corners
    * Elegant hover effects
    
    The layout should feel **premium, modern, and high-end**.
    
    ---
    
    ## Animations (Important)
    
    Animations should be **very smooth, modern, and visually impressive**, but still lightweight and performance-friendly.
    
    Include:
    
    * Smooth **scroll-triggered animations**
    * **Fade-in and slide-up effects** when sections appear
    * **Glass cards gently floating or revealing on scroll**
    * **Subtle hover animations** for cards and headings
    * **Animated section dividers**
    * Optional **parallax background effect**
    * Smooth **page transitions**
    * **Back-to-top animated button**
    * Smooth **scroll navigation**
    
    Animations should feel **premium and polished**, similar to modern tech websites.
    
    ---
    
    ## Full Customization in Shopify Theme Editor
    
    Everything should be **fully customizable without editing code** using the **Shopify Theme Editor**.
    
    Provide settings for:
    
    ### Background Options
    
    * Solid color background
    * Gradient background (multi-color)
    * Background image upload
    * Overlay opacity control
    
    ### Typography Controls
    
    * Font family selector
    * Heading font size control
    * Body text size control
    * Font weight options
    * Line spacing
    * Text color controls
    
    ### Layout Controls
    
    * Content width (narrow / medium / wide)
    * Section spacing (top & bottom padding)
    * Text alignment (left / center)
    * Card spacing controls
    
    ---
    
    ## Content Editing (Very Important)
    
    I want the **ability to write and control all the content myself** directly inside the Shopify Theme Editor.
    
    Please **do NOT hardcode any Privacy Policy text**.
    
    Instead:
    
    * Create **modular sections and blocks**
    * Allow me to **add, edit, remove, and reorder sections**
    
    Each section should include editable fields such as:
    
    * Section title
    * Subtitle (optional)
    * Rich text content
    * Optional icon
    
    The text fields should support **Shopify rich text editing** so I can format:
    
    * Paragraphs
    * Bullet lists
    * Headings
    * Links
    
    The idea is that I can **write whatever Privacy Policy content I want later**, while the developer only builds the **structure and design**.
    
    ---
    
    ## Template Structure
    
    This page should be created as a **custom Shopify template**.
    
    Inside the template:
    
    * The **glass-style sections should exist as template sections**
    * I should be able to **add multiple glass sections**
    * Each section should contain **editable text blocks**
    
    Example sections I might create later:
    
    * Hero section with page title
    * Introduction
    * Information We Collect
    * How We Use Your Information
    * Cookies & Tracking Technologies
    * Data Protection
    * Third-Party Services
    * Your Rights
    * Policy Updates
    * Contact Information
    
    Each section should support:
    
    * Rich text content
    * Optional icons
    * Scroll animations
    * Clean formatting
    
    ---
    
    ## Additional UX Features
    
    Include:
    
    * Optional **sticky side navigation or scroll progress indicator**
    * **Smooth scrolling between sections**
    * **Accordion option for sections**
    * Mobile-optimized spacing
    * Perfect readability for long legal content
    
    ---
    
    ## Performance Requirements
    
    The page must remain **fast and optimized**.
    
    * Use **Shopify Liquid + CSS + minimal JavaScript**
    * Avoid heavy libraries
    * Ensure **fast loading speed**
    * Fully compatible with **Shopify Online Store 2.0 themes**
    
    ---
    
    ## Final Goal
    
    Create a **beautiful, glass-style, highly animated Privacy Policy page** that looks modern and premium while remaining **fully customizable and easy for me to edit inside Shopify**.
    
    The developer should focus on:
    
    * Building a **stunning visual layout**
    * Adding **smooth modern animations**
    * Providing **flexible editable content blocks**
    * Keeping everything **responsive, lightweight, and customizable**.
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-privacy-glass-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    overflow-y: visible;
    {% if block.settings.background_type == 'color' %}
      background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    {% elsif block.settings.background_type == 'gradient' %}
      background: linear-gradient({{ block.settings.gradient_angle }}deg, {{ block.settings.gradient_color_1 }}, {{ block.settings.gradient_color_2 }});
    {% elsif block.settings.background_type == 'image' and block.settings.background_image %}
      background-image: url('{{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: {% if block.settings.enable_parallax %}fixed{% else %}scroll{% endif %};
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
    opacity: {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {% if block.settings.content_width == 'narrow' %}800px{% elsif block.settings.content_width == 'medium' %}1000px{% else %}1200px{% endif %};
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: {{ block.settings.glass_background }};
    backdrop-filter: blur({{ block.settings.glass_blur }}px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur({{ block.settings.glass_blur }}px);
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    border: {{ block.settings.glass_border_thickness }}px solid {{ block.settings.glass_border_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.card_spacing }}px;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.shadow_x }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_y }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_color }};
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.ai-animated-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-{{ block.settings.hover_lift }}px);
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.shadow_x }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_y | plus: 10 }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_blur | plus: 10 }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.glass_border_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-privacy-glass-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.heading_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-privacy-glass-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.body_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.body_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.body_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.body_color }};
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} ul,
  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} ol {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} a {
    color: {{ block.settings.link_color }};
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} a:hover {
    color: {{ block.settings.link_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, {{ block.settings.divider_color }}, transparent);
    margin: {{ block.settings.divider_spacing }}px 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: all 0.6s ease;
  }

  .ai-privacy-glass-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}.ai-animated-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .ai-privacy-back-to-top-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 30px;
    right: 30px;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: {{ block.settings.back_to_top_bg }};
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.back_to_top_border }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .ai-privacy-back-to-top-{{ ai_gen_id }}.ai-visible-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
  }

  .ai-privacy-back-to-top-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .ai-privacy-back-to-top-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    fill: {{ block.settings.back_to_top_icon_color }};
  }

  .ai-privacy-progress-bar-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: {{ block.settings.progress_bar_color }};
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.1s ease;
    z-index: 9999;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-privacy-glass-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.6 }}px 16px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-privacy-glass-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding | times: 0.7 }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.card_spacing | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-privacy-glass-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-privacy-glass-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-privacy-glass-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.body_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-privacy-back-to-top-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-privacy-glass-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      background-attachment: scroll !important;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

